objects.description: [APT28](https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0007) has retrieved internal documents from machines inside victim environments, including by using [Forfiles](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0193) to stage documents before.(Citation: Überwachung APT28 Forfiles June 2015)(Citation: DOJ GRU Indictment Jul 2018)
